• Advising the Ministry of Agriculture and Environment, the Ministry of Finance, and provincial authorities on the use of digitalisation including digital applications, tools and databases;
• Ensuring close and effective cooperation and communication with relevant partners and stakeholders at national and provincial level during the implementation of the activities;
